codex
I have enough to write the verifier. I’m making it path-strict: it first tries the exact `mint(X) -> contract receives < X -> burn` sequence using verifier-held underlying, and otherwise it records the concrete reason the path is not self-funding at this fork instead of pivoting to a different exploit.
